  "detailed_description": "<h1>Notification</h1><p>获得免费DLC两种方式：<br>方法1：点击链接安装 <br><br>方法2：按组合键：WIN + R 输入：steam://install/1469010 ，按ENTER键即可。<br>【WIN键在键盘左下角，标识为四个小方块的那个】<br>如遇到无法加载，在STEAM库中，鼠标右键点击“打工人的十日女友” 》 属性 》DLC 下重新勾选即可。<br><br>我们的QQ群：1004267236</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1450170/extras/733e1a31f40ba23c14468f24dcca5142.poster.avif?t=1616655976\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1450170/extras/733e1a31f40ba23c14468f24dcca5142.webm?t=1616655976\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1450170/extras/733e1a31f40ba23c14468f24dcca5142.mp4?t=1616655976\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[Background]</h2>The story takes place on a tropical island named “Highland Island”, where the Middle Age Devil died.<br>My travel gets really SPECIAL because of this mysterious island.<br>After everything shows me that I’m the son of the Devil, what I should do with my POWER? to conquer the world? or end my single life?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1450170/extras/e6a07e0c1eb178c802df0ed9b88200ea.poster.avif?t=1616655976\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1450170/extras/e6a07e0c1eb178c802df0ed9b88200ea.webm?t=1616655976\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1450170/extras/e6a07e0c1eb178c802df0ed9b88200ea.mp4?t=1616655976\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >[Game Features]</h2>1. Tropical island style of enviroment<br><br>2. Day and night changes in the game<br><br>3. Over 30 exquisite CG paintings<br><br>4. 7 different endings<br><br>5. Funny side story & funny NPC<br><br>We’ve been working hard to bring more multi-line of the story to our audience, please stay tuned for our upcoming updates, thanks.",
